  • Classes in com.eclipsesource.tabris.camera used by com.eclipsesource.tabris.camera 
    Class Description
    CameraListener
    The CameraListener is used to receive notifications from a mobile client when it's done with taking pictures.
    CameraOptions
    The CameraOptions is used to configure a Camera object when taking a picture via Camera.takePicture(CameraOptions).
    PhotoAlbumListener
    The PhotoAlbumListener is used to receive notifications from a mobile client when it's done with selecting pictures from the photo album.
    PhotoAlbumOptions
    The PhotoAlbumOptions is used to configure a PhotoAlbum object when taking a picture via PhotoAlbum.open(PhotoAlbumOptions).
